	"SettingDescriptions":{
		"Auto map": "Areas that you have the map for will automatically fill in without needing to rest at a bench or have the quill",
		"Unlock map": "Unlocks The Moss Grotto map for you, so you have access to the inventory map and sidebar",
		"Show map in abyss": "You got there!",
		"Show map in *****": "You’ll know once you get there ;-)",
		"More markers": "Gives 99 of every kind of marker",
		"Force display Hornet pin (compass)": "Force displaying Hornet’s location",
		"Highlight Hornet marker": "Shiny",
		"Icon set": "Pick your favorite icon set or create your own!",
		"Hornet marker highlight speed": "Applies to all highlight types",
		"Always show marker labels": "Normally marker labels only show when you are over the marker. This will make all labels show all the time.",
		"Icon/Marker size": "The size of the icons on the map",
		"Icon/Marker size scales with zoom": "If true icons will always stay the same size at any zoom.",
		"Found icon color*": "When in “All” mode for a category, found icons are tinted this color.\nRGB is actually HSV [Hue Saturation Lightness], unless the shader fails to load, in which case, it really is RGB.",
		"Hornet marker: Revolving: Distance": "The distance of the revolutions",
		"Hornet marker: Revolving: Is Clockwise": "The direction of the revolving",
		"Hornet marker: Growing: Max Size": "The largest the growing effect gets",
		"Hornet marker: Spinning: Is Clockwise": "The direction of the spinning",
		"Hornet marker: Rainbow 1: Scale": "The zoom-scale of the 256 color gradient texture. This basically dictates how many color bands you can see at a time (higher=more).",
		"Hornet marker: Rainbow 2: Wait time": "The time in between rainbow 2 effects",
		"Hornet marker: Rainbow 2: Run time": "The time the rainbow 2 effects run",
		"Marker Pan Speed": "Normally, the left stick pan speed is 7, with the right stick doubled. However, since the right stick is taken by other functions now, I put this at 14.",
		"Unlock map bounds": "This is needed due to zooming issues and the sidebar covering the map",
		"Marker Zoom No Move-Reset": "Normally, when you go in and out of marker mode, it resets the map position to the middle of the map you are actually on. With this turned on, it doesn’t reset the map position.",
		"Show downloaded icon pictures": "When you select an icon on the map, show the images from mapgenie.io on the sidebar.",
		"Show mouse with sidebar/search": "Shows the mouse when the sidebar or search window are visible",
		"Shortcut Key: Execute selected item": "Executes the selected button/group/category on the sidebar.",
		"Shortcut Key: Select icon": "When the sidebar and marker modes are active, pressing this will ‘select’ the icon you are over",
		"Shortcut Key: Show/hide the window": "Toggle the value window. See help or mod page for more information.",
		"Persistent Object Query Time": "How often in seconds to query persistent data value changes (separate thread). There are never more than ~50 objects per scene (more usually like 10), and current value queries are usually really simple, so this doesn’t take a lot of processing. Honestly, these could probably run every frame just fine.",
		"Player Data Query Time": "How often in seconds to query player data value changes (separate thread). There are over 1200 reflection lookups for this so query time is less often. Honestly, these could probably run every frame just fine.",
		"Category States": "DO NOT EDIT THIS. List of categories and their toggle states.",
		"Marker Labels": "DO NOT EDIT THIS. List of marker labels",
	},
