		"Scroll this window with Sidebar Scroll Up/Down": "Scroll this window with Sidebar Scroll Up/Down",
		"HelpText": "<title>General notes:</title>\n* Configs are saved per-user-saveslot with backups.\n* Features disabled by default (press <b>F1</b> for config): Auto map, Unlock map, More markers, and Force compass display\n\n<title>Input Devices:</title>\n* Fully supports <b>keyboard</b>, <b>mouse</b>, and <b>controller</b>. <size=15>(except <b>search window</b>: mouse/keyboard only)</size>.\n* <configs><conf>Show mouse with sidebar/search</conf></configs>\n\n<title>Map Features</title>\n* Excludes fully zoomed-out area-name (wide) view.\n* Auto-unlock mapped areas (without bench) <config>Auto map</config>.\n* Early map access <config>Unlock map</config>.\n\n<subtitle>Icons:</subtitle>\n* Shows all notable locations as icons. Toggle visibility via Sidebar categories.\n* <configs><conf>Icon/Marker size</conf>, <conf>Icon/Marker size scales with zoom</conf></configs>\n\n<subtitle>Markers:</subtitle>\n* Marker mode always available.\n* More markers <config>More markers</config>.\n* Marker labels\n	* <configs><conf>Always show marker labels</conf>, <conf>Shortcut: Edit Marker Label</conf></configs>\n* Force display Hornet pin <config>Force display Hornet pin (compass)</config>\n* Show map in <ABYSS> <config>Show map in *****</config>\n* Make Hornet marker more visible\n	* <configs><conf>Highlight Hornet marker</conf>, <conf>Hornet marker highlight speed</conf>, <conf><b>Lots more under advanced settings</b></conf></configs>\n* Visual marker label<configs><conf>Marker label text color</conf>, <conf>Marker label background color</conf></configs>\n* Toggle markers via right click\n\n<subtitle>Hover & Select</subtitle>\n* <b>Marker-mode</b>:\n	* Enter by pressing the “A” button again after opening the map (when you can add in-game colored markers).\n	* Move marker selector as normal; hovered icon turns <color=blue>blue</color>.\n* Mouse-over hover in both modes.\n* Hovered icon name appears atop Sidebar.\n* Select (mouse click or “<b><color=purple>Y</color></b>”): Turns <color=green>green</color>, shows images/info in Sidebar.\n	* <configs><conf>Show downloaded icon pictures</conf></configs>\n* Last-moved input (mouse/selector) determines hover.\n\n<subtitle><color=cyan><u>Zoom:</u></color></subtitle>\n* Scroll wheel: Around mouse cursor. Always available.\n* Non-Marker Mode: Around screen center.\n* Marker Mode: Around hovered icon (or selector center if none).\n* <configs><conf>Zoom Speed</conf>, <conf>Marker Zoom No Move-Reset</conf></configs>\n\n<subtitle>Pan:</subtitle>\n* Bounds unlocked by default <config>Unlock map bounds</config>—essential for sidebar overlap and zoom.\n* <configs><conf>Pan Speed</conf>, <conf>Marker Pan Speed</conf></configs>\n* Recenter over character: “<b><color=yellow>X</color></b>”\n* Mouse drag also to pan.\n\n<title>Sidebar:</title>\n* Icon category states (cycle via click):\n	1. <b>Show All</b>: Shows all icons. Found icons are translucent+gray.\n	2. Show Incomplete: Non-bold text; Non-found icons only.\n	3. <s>Hide all</s>: No icons.\n* Group headers cycle all sub-categories.\n* Hover/select icons shows info at top (see “<b>Hover & Select</b>”).\n* “Toggle groups” buttons: Set all categories to chosen state.\n* “Show Linked” button: Unlinked icons (haven’t been linked to a save value) become <color=red>red</color> (see “<b>Values Window</b>”).\n* <configs><conf>Starts open on game load</conf>, <conf>Shortcut key: Show/hide the sidebar</conf></configs>\n* Visual (sidebar)<configs><conf>Background color</conf>, <conf>Interface items color</conf>, <conf>Highlight color</conf>, <conf>Width</conf></configs>\n\n<title>Values Window:</title>\n* Log of changed save values (newest top). Window can persist without opened map.\n* Use to link icons to save names (e.g., benches often under “*Remasker*”) to show if already found on map.\n* Link the selected (green) icon: “Save” → local JSON; “Save+Send” → Also crowdsources to author.\n\n<title>Search Window:</title>\n* Searches titles, categories, and descriptions (space-separated AND).\n* Results: 7-line preview + ellipsis if longer; full on hover.\n* Click on result: Selects and centers map over icon.",
	},
